<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, December 26 (Xinhua) -- The 5th session of the
United Arab Emirates (UAE)-Egyptian joint committee, ended in
Dubai today after deciding to affirm bilateral coordination on
labor and technical cooperation.
</P>
