a move to step up the country's anti-corruption campaign.
</P>
<P>
Zhang Siqing, procurator-general of the Superme People's
Procuratorate (SPP), made the remark today in Beijing at the
closing ceremony of a five-day National Procurators' Conference.
</P>
<P>
