will further hamper the development of the country's fledgling
insurance industry if no solutions are found, according to the
official.
</P>
<P>
The methods for founding a new farming insurance network are
still under consideration, but the new agricultural insurers are
expected to be run locally and adopt a cooperative system in terms
of administration and management, he noted. 
