330 million yuan (about 39.8 million US dollars), and the
transformer power station, which has adopted the advanced control
and protection system, are crucial to the economic development of
the 30-square-kilometer Yangpu Development Zone.
</P>
<P>
The zone is the first area China has offered to investors from
overseas for large-tract development.
</P>
<P>
