graduating students before considering their appointment," said an
employer.
</P>
<P>
The school, under the Chinese Academy of Sciences, is one of
the leading universities in the country.
</P>
<P>
Since 1984, the school has sent people around the country to
introduce its gradutes to institutes and enterprises in need of
personnel.
</P>
<P>
This time, it invited employers to its campus to have closer
contacts with their future employees.
</P>
<P>
After years of efforts, the school has established stable
contacts with more than 70 employers.
</P>
<P>
From 1992 to 1996, 90 percent of the graduates find employment
through job fairs, according to the university. 
