Concerted efforts are being made by Taiwan businesses to
establish specialized production centers in Zhejiang.
</P>
<P>
The Taiwan Machinery Industrial Park in Xiaoshan and the Toy
Industrial Park in Yuyao are good examples, co-funded by more than
100 Taiwan businesses.
</P>
<P>
More investment from Taiwan-funded enterprises is being put
into technology-intensive industries like electronics and chemical
fibres.  
